# Project core

- **Stack:** React 19, TypeScript, Vite 8, ESLint 10, Prettier 3
- **Shared agent instructions:** [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)
- **Skills:** `.agents/skills/` (canonical); Cursor also reads `.cursor/skills/` and `.claude/skills/` when present
- **Scripts:** `npm run dev`, `build`, `lint`, `preview`

Keep changes minimal and match existing conventions. Config files tagged `@agent-maintain` are comments-only unless the user asks to change values.
